<div class="com-share" data-id="10328" data-title="《喜欢造梦的诺兰说，年轻人你现实一点》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/10328/medium/10328.jpg?1436649758" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/10328.html?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
